::Spears::

She walked to the computer room.  She went to a panel in the back and 
started repairs.  She pulled three panels off the wall and a small 
panel with it.  She ripped out a bunch of burnt wires and power boxes 
that had been fried.  She went to take one panel that was just above 
her head.  She pulled on it and a whole side of the wall fell down on 
her.  She screamed,"AHHHHHHH!"  She put her arms above her head and 
stood still.

When it had stopped and the soot died down, she was now covered head 
to toe with blask soot and grime.  She stood there for a moment then 
called out,"FOR THE LOVE OF THE MARTIX, THIS JUST ISN'T MY DAY!"
She sighed and looked about.  She looked around hoping to see a 
shovel to remove the junk that surraounded her.
